**Project Name:** HeadphoneHub  
**Description:** A modern, responsive website for showcasing premium headphones with dual theme functionality  
**Technology Stack:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)  
**Developer:** Akarsh Chaturvedi  
**Repository:** https://github.com/AkarshYash/HeadphoneHub  

## ðŸŽ¯ Core Requirements

### 1. THEME SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
- [x] Dual theme support (Light & Dark modes)
- [x] Theme toggle button with icons (sun/moon)
- [x] Automatic theme detection from system preferences
- [x] Local storage for theme persistence
- [x] Smooth transitions between themes
- [x] Consistent color scheme across all elements

### 2. DESIGN & UI/UX REQUIREMENTS
- [x] Fully responsive design (mobile-first approach)
- [x] Modern, professional appearance
- [x] Gradient color schemes
